          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/OttiBlack.png",
            "title": "Otti Australia",
            "text": "<p>At Cook & Bathe, we proudly showcase the Otti Collection – a brand that exemplifies the fusion of elegant design and everyday functionality. Whether you're updating a <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/pages/bathroom-range\"><strong>bathroom</strong></a>, or designing a new build; Otti offers an exceptional range of <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/basins\"><strong>basins</strong></a><strong>, </strong><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/mirrors\"><strong>mirrors</strong></a><strong>, </strong><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/baths\"><strong>baths</strong></a>, and <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/vanity-units\"><strong>vanities</strong></a>, that reflect the latest in modern Australian home styling.<br/></p>",
            "link_label": "Otti Australia",
            "link": "shopify://collections/otti"
          }
        },
        "column_k4DiEn": {
          "type": "column",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Fienza.png",
            "title": "Fienza",
            "text": "<p>Step into a world where form meets function. Welcome to Cook & Bathe's exclusive collection of <a href=\"/collections/fienza\" title=\"Fienza\"><strong>Fienza bathroom products</strong></a>, where every piece tells a story. Our selection, ranging from <a href=\"/collections/fienza-vanities\" title=\"Fienza Vanities\"><strong>Vanities</strong></a><strong> and </strong><a href=\"/collections/fienza-basins\" title=\"Fienza Basins\"><strong>Basins </strong></a><strong>to </strong><a href=\"/collections/fienza-tapware\" title=\"Fienza Tapware\"><strong>Sink Mixers</strong></a><strong>, showers, bath mixers, and pop-up waste</strong>, embodies the art of living well.<br/></p>",
            "link_label": "Fienza Bathware",
            "link": "shopify://collections/fienza"
          }
        }
      },
