    "image_with_text_EDKXGR": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_VrkJxB": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Otti Vanities & Shaving Cabinets: The full solution",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_Yj4mcy": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>With the Modern Australian Home in mind, Otti Australia’s collection and combinations of Vanities, Shaving Cabinets and Basins create a beautiful and detailed space for any home.</p><p>Each piece in the Otti range is crafted with a deep understanding of contemporary Australian interiors—balancing minimalist lines with rich, organic textures and functional storage. Whether you’re looking for a sleek wall-hung vanity to enhance a compact ensuite or a bold floor-standing unit to anchor a family bathroom, Otti offers versatile options to suit every need.</p><p>Their shaving cabinets are more than just mirrors—they provide smart, integrated storage with soft-close doors and optional LED lighting for added luxury. With sizes ranging from 600mm to 1200mm and finishes like matte white, charcoal oak, and natural oak, these pieces are designed to harmonise with a wide range of bathroom aesthetics.</p><p>Built for durability with moisture-resistant materials and seamless ceramic basins, Otti vanities and cabinets are a trusted choice for renovators, interior designers, and homeowners seeking quality without compromise.</p><p>Explore the full Otti Australia collection today and elevate your bathroom with modern elegance, practical design, and enduring quality—available online or in-store at Cook & Bathe.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
