    "image_with_text_xngRVJ": {
      "type": "image-with-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_WUHCbr": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Fienza Bathware",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_EjqKGg": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>With a reputation built on precision, innovation, and bold design, Fienza delivers bathroom furniture that makes a statement. Their vanities and shaving cabinets are not just functional—they’re focal points. Created for homeowners who value contemporary detail and architectural flair, each piece offers a refined take on everyday bathroom essentials.</p><p>Fienza vanities feature strong geometric forms, textured finishes, and fluted or ribbed detailing that adds depth and drama to any space. Whether you're selecting a floating vanity for a clean, modern look or a structured floor-mounted design for added presence, Fienza’s options are designed to align with current interior trends—while delivering day-to-day performance.</p><p>Shaving cabinets in the Fienza collection are equally striking. Framed or frameless, mirrored or matte, with optional open shelving and soft-close mechanisms—they’re designed to complement modern lifestyles while elevating the overall aesthetic of the bathroom.</p><p>Highlights include:</p><ul><li>On-trend finishes including timber, matte white, and deep oak.</li><li>Optional brushed gold or matte black handles for a designer touch.</li><li>Fluted and V-Groove door designs for texture and dimensions.</li><li>Durable, moisture-resistant construction built for Australian conditions.</li><li>Customisable widths and configurations to suit any space.</li></ul><p>Fienza is the brand of choice for those designing high-impact bathrooms with purpose and personality. Whether you're starting fresh or upgrading a dated space, explore Fienza’s bold bathroom furniture range today online at Cook & Bathe, or visit our Melbourne showroom for expert guidance.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
