    "rich_text_Renqx7": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_YYwPtj": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<h2>Why Australian Homes Choose Quality Vanities</h2>",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_hxw6mn": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At <strong>Cook & Bathe</strong>, we know vanities are more than just bathroom furniture; they’re a balance of design, storage, and daily ease in demanding Australian conditions. With decades of experience supplying trusted brands like <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/ott\" title=\"Otti Australia Collection\">Otti Australia</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/fienza\" title=\"Fienza bathware collection\">Fienza</a>, we select vanities built for moisture resilience, long-lasting finishes, and seamless style integration. Whether you're renovating a family bathroom, updating a compact ensuite, or creating a spa-like retreat, we're your go‑to partner for expertise, reliable delivery across Australia, and exceptional post-purchase support.<br/><br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "heading_V8JDzn": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<h3>Timeless Styles Powered by Local Expertise</h3>",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_eKf8xY": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Discover inspiration from our <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/blogs/news/get-inspired-9-styles-we-cant-get-enough-of\" title=\"9 Styles We Can’t Get Enough Of\">“9 Styles We Can’t Get Enough Of”</a> blog—covering design themes from coastal minimalism to modern maximalism, boutique hotel vibes to classic Hamptons chic. Our curated collections make it easy to match your décor:</p><ul><li>For a sleek minimalist look, choose a handle-free <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/wall-hung\" title=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/wall-hung\">wall-hung vanity.</a></li><li>Love texture or visual depth? Try <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/fienza\" title=\"Fienza Bathware Fluted Vanity\">fluted-front vanities</a> in timber finishes from Fienza.</li></ul><p>We link these style inspirations directly into our <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/vanity-units\" title=\"Cook & Bathe Vanity collection\">Vanity Units</a> range, along with tapware, mirrors and basins, creating one cohesive design journey for your bathroom.<br/></p>"
          }
        },
        "heading_TTtVdd": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<h3>Smart Storage and Practical Performance<br/></h3>",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_tjHJGA": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Ideal storage solutions matter—soft-close drawers, adjustable shelving, integrated basins and concealed plumbing access ensure your vanity works as hard as it looks. Many models offer standard dimensions (600 mm, 750 mm, 900 mm, 1200 mm)—perfectly suited to Australian building standards and typical bathroom layouts. Our experts help you avoid costly mistakes by matching units to plumbing spaces and style requirements before purchase.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
