    "rich_text_HemrCg": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_AFn8CN": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<h3>Trends Tailored for Australian Homes in 2025</h3>",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_rE6Xrd": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>As part of our Bathroom Trends 2025 Collection, we’ve layered storewide trends into our vanity offer—like water-conscious basins, eco-friendly finishes, and combined aesthetic features pulled through from modern kitchens to bathrooms. Pair your vanity with archival-style tapware or brushed-gold fixtures for a timeless finish, drawing from our blog inspiration on:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/blogs/news/get-inspired-9-styles-we-cant-get-enough-of\">Interior Styles</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/blogs/news/outside-in\">Bringing the Outside In</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/blogs/news/brushed-gold-finding-your-style-with-stunning-flatlays\">Brushed Gold Styling Inspiration</a><br/><br/></li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "heading_UhJmhc": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<h3>Complete Your Bathroom with Complementary Collections</h3>",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_FBqwwt": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>To build a fully coordinated space, consider:</p><ul><li><a href=\"/collections/basins-and-sinks\" title=\"Basins and Sinks\">Basins</a>: sleek integrated-top basins, designer ceramic styles and countertop bowls</li><li><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/tapware-bathroom\">Tapware & Bathroom Accessories</a>: match your vanity with stylish tapware and finishes</li><li><a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/collections/mirrors\">Mirrors</a>: round, pill, LED-lit and arched options to enhance both light and design flow</li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "heading_4fUGk3": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "<h2>Your Renovation Partner, from Concept to Completion</h2>",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_w6BCNw": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Our <a href=\"https://www.cookandbathe.com.au/pages/store-locations\">Melbourne showrooms</a> are grounded in style advice and hands-on product viewing—serving renovators, designers and homeowners nationwide. We offer expert help choosing the right vanity for your style, functionality needs and room dimensions. Shop confidently with free Australia-wide delivery, full product specs, expert design guides and exceptional post-sale support.<br/><br/>Embrace functional luxury built for Australian bathrooms—from streamlined wall-hung designs to bold floor-standing vanities and smart shaving cabinets; only at Cook & bathe.<br/><br/></p>"
          }
        }
      },
